    "CNNs are specifically designed to work with images, and its basic building block is relatively simple convolutional filters.",
    "First, CNN architecture can be utilized to explain visual artefacts created by CNN-based decoders.",
    "Second, CNN-based decoders can only output images of low quality (512×512px in the Cycle-GAN).",
    "CycleGAN, which trains generators utilizing an encoder-decoder architecture and cycle reliability.",
    "However, these choices are not without challenges."
